That's the story... Mercedes bought out VAZ
Production has started, the first car is coming off - KALINA ...
The equipment has been reconfigured, KALINA again...
We increased the staff of engineers, changed all the equipment, the workers underwent additional training and again the KALINA comes off the assembly line ...
Not far from the plant, the former director and the chief engineer are sitting on a hill, drinking beer and the chief engineer without irony to the director:
- I told you - it's a damn place!
